### Crystalline BTO; calculation of physical structure contstants

###
# Structure Specification Vars
###

## Unit Cell
#rprim DEFAULT
acell 3*4 angstrom # a = 3.995, c = 4.034 Ãƒ

## Atom Positions
ntypat 3        # Ba, Ti, O, resp.
znucl 56 22 8

natom 5
typat 1 2 3 3 3 # Ba, Ti, 3O
xred
  0.0 0.0 0.0   # Ba
  1/2 1/2 1/2   # Ti
  0.0 1/2 1/2   # O 1 yz
  1/2 0.0 1/2   # O 2 xz
  1/2 1/2 0.0   # O 3 xy

###
# Structure Optimization Vars
###

ionmov 2        # consider 3 instead if there are fewer than 5 DoF to consider
ntime 15        # the # of time step to use in the optimization cycle
tolmxf 5.0e-6   # force tolerance below which relaxation itrs stop. i.e., can end calc before 'ntime' itrs are reached. In Ha/Bohr
toldff 5.0e-7   # see above but for the scf cycle rather than the relaxation cycle

